name: Cyc… no, wait… go mushrooming 2019
description:
============= FACTS =============

MEETING POINT: 09:40 at the ticket machine right after the NORTHERN entrance in S-Bahnhof Yorckstraße for S2 OR on the first train compartment of the S-Bahn OR in Karow when switching trains!
TICKET: Berlin-Brandenburg-Ticket when you sign up for it (Details below), otherwise its on your own
REQUIREMENTS: NO bike but social behaviou
